OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1778094687
OL,3,CRabbit halts flights as it hops onto
OL,4,Crunway
OL,6,FFlights were briefly halted at Jersey
OL,7,FAirport after a rabbit hopped onto the
OL,8,Fisland's runway.
OL,10,FA member of staff was quickly
OL,11,Fdispatched with a box to rescue the
OL,12,Fanimal, which had stopped in front of
OL,13,Fa light aircraft at around 10:30am on
OL,14,FTuesday (5 May).
OL,16,FBecky Sheeran was a passenger on the
OL,17,Fdeparting BA1347 flight bound for
OL,18,FLondon Heathrow, which was held up by
OL,19,Fthe unexpected visitor.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/3
