PN,38602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1778094687
OL,3,CRabbit halts flights as it hops onto
OL,4,Crunway
OL,6,FShe explains: "It was really funny.
OL,7,FThe pilot made an announcement to say
OL,8,Fwe were being held up because of a
OL,9,Frabbit and to look out of our window,
OL,10,Fas no planes could take off until it
OL,11,Fhad been caught.
OL,13,F"I think it was around 20 minutes we
OL,14,Fwere held on the runway and no planes
OL,15,Fcould take off."
OL,17,FThe rabbit was safely moved to allow
OL,18,Fservices to resume, with only minor
OL,19,Fdelays.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/3
